    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. CFD predictions of hemolysis index agree with experimental data within 8.4% mean absolute error across all operating points, and the relative hemolysis index satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion for all five flow-speed combinations. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II device.",
